  "summary": "IDF reported hostile aircraft alerts and engaged a Hezbollah launcher, intercepting rockets and destroying a suspect vehicle in south Lebanon. Israeli jets bombed the outskirts of Kafr Tebnit in southern Lebanon. Iran accused Israel of multiple cease‑fire violations in the same area.",
