    "executive_summary": "IDF alerts for hostile aircraft and a direct engagement with Hezbollah assets in south Lebanon highlight escalating border tensions. Israeli airstrikes on Kafr Tebnit further intensify the conflict. Iran’s accusations of cease‑fire breaches and threats of retaliation add a broader regional dimension.",
